Title: Sequence Diagram for Food Ordering Process

User -> Application: Select restaurant and add dishes to cart
User -> Application: Place order and choose payment method
Application -> Payment Gateway: Process payment
Payment Gateway -> Application: Payment confirmed
Application -> Restaurant: Send order details
Restaurant -> Application: Order accepted and being prepared
Restaurant -> Courier: Order is ready for pickup
Courier -> Application: Order picked up
Courier -> User: Deliver order
User -> Application: Confirm order receipt
